    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这已经让你感到疲惫不堪。城市生活的喧嚣与忙碌从未停歇。无论你走到哪里，都仿佛被无尽的人潮所包围，而这些人又像变形虫般不断变换形态，却又让你感到无比孤独。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为刚在乡下买下一座老农场的都市人佩德罗·贝塔索，你决定了既然要独自生活，不如与大自然的宁静和诚实勤劳为伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，事情并没有完全按照佩德罗的计划进行。一些……事情很快打乱了他的宁静与孤独。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建造你的农场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/fc504d68f3b74fd7ddc23946c5361912.poster.avif?t=1758878460\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/fc504d68f3b74fd7ddc23946c5361912.webm?t=1758878460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/fc504d68f3b74fd7ddc23946c5361912.mp4?t=1758878460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过选择多种种子，在你的农场种植多种作物。你的小规模经营将与你耕耘的田地共同成长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >努力工作以维持生计，然后逐步扩展—修复你的新家，发展畜牧业，投资于能够让收割季节更加轻松的升级项目。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>直面萦绕的阴魂</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/e9279b9a6c5de37fc5e657411cd7c8be.poster.avif?t=1758878460\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/e9279b9a6c5de37fc5e657411cd7c8be.webm?t=1758878460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/e9279b9a6c5de37fc5e657411cd7c8be.mp4?t=1758878460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会欢迎这些轻松的时光，因为它们实在太少太稀有了。这座农场确实出了大问题，即便前主人没有向佩德罗隐瞒这一事实，他们也肯定无法解释清楚。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夜幕降临，诡异的声音从漆黑的深处传来，随着时间的推移，情况愈发恶劣。这些声音的来源逐渐显现，并变得愈发凶猛。集结武器，为生存而战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>优化你的工作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/62bbd0d2fc33b025ec5c5839097be6bb.poster.avif?t=1758878460\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/62bbd0d2fc33b025ec5c5839097be6bb.webm?t=1758878460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/62bbd0d2fc33b025ec5c5839097be6bb.mp4?t=1758878460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在市场上出售你的农作物，购买新的工具和车辆，以优化你在田间的作业。坚持不懈地工作，平衡好你的耕作努力与防御措施，很快你就能用真正的联合收割机取代你的镰刀。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>乡村恐怖故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/732669cea98ddb3094275ed25c48697b.poster.avif?t=1758878460\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/732669cea98ddb3094275ed25c48697b.webm?t=1758878460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/732669cea98ddb3094275ed25c48697b.mp4?t=1758878460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但这种情况不能再继续下去了，而逃跑在这种情况下根本不是一个选项。如果佩德罗不尽快弄清楚到底发生了什么，那些盘踞在这片土地上的生物很快就会让他命丧黄泉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与世隔绝，置身于一片广袤的开阔地带，你隐约感到在这片荒芜与残骸之中，必定隐藏着某种特殊的存在—某种不祥之物，正是这一切的根源……</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索开放领域</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/a3c459772801076ad40f36e24d0652e8.poster.avif?t=1758878460\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/a3c459772801076ad40f36e24d0652e8.webm?t=1758878460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/a3c459772801076ad40f36e24d0652e8.mp4?t=1758878460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你想成功，就必须彻底搜查周围的每一个角落。佩德罗的努力一定会得到回报，不仅是知识，还有珍贵的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索农场的诡异过往，通过漫游开阔的乡村地区收集资源。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>解锁新的领域</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/ffa6a0a7a1b52b901d359aef80a289df.poster.avif?t=1758878460\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/ffa6a0a7a1b52b901d359aef80a289df.webm?t=1758878460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437790/extras/ffa6a0a7a1b52b901d359aef80a289df.mp4?t=1758878460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买新区域以扩展你的农场，并解锁新物品和载具。但要小心—这些地方潜伏的生物可不欢迎你的反抗。随着新田地的开辟，你必然会遭遇新的恐惧……</p>",
